db70d4729ac86db53d9d949b54a8337c04b16971","tid":1594793,"uid":326806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"話說早幾日去果欄搵香印青提子<br />\n係內巷行左幾間不停聽到d 叔叔阿姨討論話班手足搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令到佢地生意唔好經濟唔好 又乜又7<br />\n所以一直行過冇幫襯！好L著<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到去到一間冇咩聲既走埋去睇下，之後問個丫姐點賣邊d靚<br />\n之後無啦啦丫姐hi 7我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識買唔好搞L亂曬啦！揀老婆咩！你d後生日日貪玩搞亂檔！香港人比你地玩死！讀死書！<br />\n之後我未出聲，隔離有位手足即刻hi返佢：玩乜L丫！知唔知我地為左唔敢上街既人爭取同發聲有幾L多人受傷丫！（我估佢真前缐）<br />\n<br />\n之後丫姐企硬～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d警察都好慘Y，冇你地警察唔洗加班可以返去陪屋企人丫！個個都有家庭丫福街仔！ 冇人要你地爭取丫～邊個叫你地丫！？<br />\n<br />\n我見再咁落去應該開拖之後同手足講冷靜冷靜～買生果姐由佢<br />\n我答左句丫姐～警察可能好慘但如果香港冇自由就唔止咁少人好慘。今日唔明他朝一日你會明。<br />\n<br />\n之後同果位手足離開～ 個丫姐大叫發瘟！ （間野叫大眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n係差不多離開既時候係街口見到有間有香印青提 （有利果欄）<br />\n我諗住黎到都要買求L其拎一包就買<br />\n神奇既事發生左<br />\n<br />\n個肥肥既丫叔同我講 頭先好嘈喎入面<br />\n我話係丫～個丫姐燥底<br />\n之後肥叔叔將我包青提換左第二包<br />\n佢話：呢包靚d丫～～ 加油啦年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當堂呆L左<br />\n<br />\n跟手佢好正經： 或者唔會個個認同你地所做既事，但最緊要你地知做緊乜嘢。 如果我好似你地咁後生我都上前衝佢LM<br />\n但似終年紀大左跑唔快又有家庭。<br />\n多謝你地！（利申我不是前線）<br />\n呢排水晶利靚拎2個返去食！<br />\n<br />\n我果下感動到淚奔<br />\n<br />\n臨走同佢講左聲： 一齊加油！<br />\n<br />\n佢比左個手指公我<br />\n<br />\n我發誓以後落去只會去肥叔叔到買生果！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\